description: If anyone in Anchorage ever has any epicurean hankerings, the big green Urban Bamboo truck knows just what to do...serve its incredible international cuisine, of course!With an emphasis on quality and local sustainability, Chef John D’Elia is dishing out a deliciously eclectic selection of sandwiches (including the Bamboo B.L.T. with braised bacon, pickled jalapeno mayo, lettuce, and tomato on a sweet Hawaiian roll), rice bowls (with your choice of Kalbi Prime Rib, Bombay Chicken, Braised Bacon, or Veggies), soups du jour, and more...and of course, everyone who tries this delightful variety, adores every bite. So for food that fuels your body and imagination, Urban Bamboo is totally the truck for you.
name: Urban Bamboo
